        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Federal Employees and Retirees with Delinquent Tax Debt Initiative (FERDI) Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Internal Revenue Service to submit to specified congressional committees and make public online an annual report on current and retired federal civilian and military employees who have delinquent tax debt or an unfiled tax return for the most recent fiscal year.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
